nodes.text: ZX-199  was an elite Skytrooper, a type of battle droid used by the Eternal Empire of Zakuul. In 3631 BBY, it was destroyed by Lana Beniko and The Commander inside the skytrooper droid factory on Zakuul.
ZX-199 appears in Star Wars: The Old Republic: Knights of the Fallen Empire Chapter 3: Outlander.
